data.description: This home is a true masterpiece, with elegant fixtures and a spacious layout. Tile flooring as you walk in, with an office space at the entrance.  The main bedroom on the 1st floor offers convenience  and with his and her vanity, garden tub and separate shower stall, walk in closet  with custom built drawers ,upstairs theater room is perfect for entertainment and loft to create a great gaming area. High ceilings create a grand atmosphere, and the covered patio is a lovely spot to enjoy your morning coffee and great spot to entertain guest. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!  ** Open House ** November /17/2023  10:00 Am - 1:00 Pm
